summary: Replaces Enderal's Well_Traveled One set with Crimson Ranger armor by patobek.
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#00ff00][size=2][color=#cc0000][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25832/?][color=#f4f4f4]With this mod,Enderal'[color=#ffffff]s[/color][/color][/url][/color][/size][/color][color=#00ff00][color=#ffffff][size=2] ragtag Well-Traveled set is replaced with the black version of the amazing Crimson Ranger armor.


[u][color=#ffff00]Version 1.1[/color][/u] fixes a very minor issue really,where a type of civilian gloves and the Well Travelled one set,shared the same model (so you could see various NPCs wear the set's gloves with their casual outfits).
